title: Bug 114470[Smoke] Error message throws when using new Date('3/2/2005') as value in table filter.
OB: When using the value new Date('3/2/2005') as input in a table filter, an error message is thrown.
EB: The table filter should accept the value new Date('3/2/2005') without throwing an error.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:  
1. Open the table filter  
2. Enter the value new Date('3/2/2005') in the filter field  
3. Press Enter  
4. Observe the error message thrown
